title: 255 - The Failure Formula
description: "Focus on the process." Those are the words of Jayda, ET's daughter, on today's podcast.  2020 has been a year like no other. COVID-19 has changed everything, and it's easy to feel like your goals and dreams have been left behind. Listen up because today, the guys differentiate between two major types of people and how they plan and execute their goals. Be prepared to take lots of notes because you don't want to miss any of the life-changing actionable tips and strategies they are dropping today.
